      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I'm not in a \"crisis\" exactly, I'm just being realistic. Like, you keep saying I shouldn't feel this way, but it's the only thing that actually makes sense. If the \"me\" that mattered is gone, then what am I even doing here? It feels like I'm just a ghost haunting my own life. It's exhausting trying to pretend there's still someone inside this shell.",
